sequenceDiagram
  participant User
  participant Map
  participant Bounds as ActivePanBoundsContext
  participant Wrapper as PersistentMapWrapper
  participant API as /api/map-listings

  User->>Map: Pan or zoom
  Map->>Bounds: Set active pan bounds
  Wrapper->>Bounds: Read active bounds
  Wrapper->>API: Fetch map listings
  API-->>Wrapper: SearchMapState
  Wrapper-->>Map: Render marker data
